cp|red|at|^*bOliverC:^*n|cp||at|  Hi Everyone and welcome to today's session, in which we're going to continue looking at various artificial defences.

Specifically, we're going to look at Defences to Pre-empts, Defences to Transfer Pre-empts, Defences to 2-suited Overcalls, and Defences to the Multi 2@d.

Some of these situations may be comparatively rare for you but it's worth being prepared nonetheless.

Needless to say, these defences can apply and be used whatever system you yourselves are playing.

Similarly, these defences do not come as a "job lot", and I make no claims that these are definitely "the best" available in a given situation. 

You are free to cherry-pick any that you feel have worth to you and your partner.

If you have not already done so, please have a look at the notes I have prepared on Precision Club bidding.

You can find these on:   ^*h http:bbo.pigpen.org.uk ^*n   

You might want to have these on screen in the background for reference during the session.

The notes on these defences can be found at ^*h http://bbo.pigpen.org.uk/Defences.php ^*n|
